{
  "description": "Merge and Conquer: SP8192 + XSA-all + MuonEq-R + QK-Gain 5.25 + Self-Gen GPTQ + EMA + Score-First TTT",
  "base": "2026-04-12_SP8192_HessMix_BrotliSWA_Coprime",
  "techniques": [
    "SP8192 tokenizer (Maximum tokens per byte for optimal BPB)",
